					<description><![CDATA[The story started 4 years ago today.  7 books have been drafted, and 3 books are already published.  It is so time to party.  That&#8217;s right, Book Three is out today! Get your copy of Clockwork Twist : Dreamer now! The eBook is on sale for $3.99. Just click the logo of your choice.   [&#8230;]]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-2618" src="http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/1-lit-01.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="445" srcset="http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/1-lit-01.jpg 1000w, http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/1-lit-01-300x222.jpg 300w, http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/1-lit-01-618x458.jpg 618w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" /></p>
<p>The story started 4 years ago today.  7 books have been drafted, and 3 books are already published.  It is so time to party.  That&#8217;s right, Book Three is out today!</p>
<h4 style="text-align: center;">Get your copy of Clockwork Twist : Dreamer now!</h4>
<p style="text-align: center;">The eBook is on sale for $3.99. Just click the logo of your choice.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.amazon.com/Clockwork-Twist-Dreamer-Emily-Thompson-ebook/dp/B00P1JG9LY" target="_blank"><img decoding="async" class="alignnone" src="http://i1.wp.com/media.corporate-ir.net/media_files/irol/17/176060/KindleLogos/Kindlelogo/scr2555-proj697-a-kindle-logo-rgb-lg.jpg?resize=148%2C40" alt="" width="148" height="40" /></a> <a href="http://www.smashwords.com/books/view/488847" target="_blank"><img decoding="async" class="alignnone" src="https://dwtr67e3ikfml.cloudfront.net/static/1/swlogo.png" alt="" width="160" height="43" /></a></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">The paperback is also available, on Amazon.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.amazon.com/Clockwork-Twist-Dreamer-Volume-3/dp/1503093832" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="http://i1.wp.com/library.corporate-ir.net/library/17/176/176060/mediaitems/93/a.com_logo_RGB.jpg?resize=181%2C53" alt="" width="181" height="53" /></a></p>
<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-2616 alignright" src="http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/1-Books-01-242x300.jpg" alt="" width="242" height="300" srcset="http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/1-Books-01-242x300.jpg 242w, http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/1-Books-01-618x765.jpg 618w, http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/1-Books-01.jpg 807w" sizes="(max-width: 242px) 100vw, 242px" />I&#8217;m just so amazed that the story has already come this far.  When I first started writing Waking, I thought I knew a thing or two about publishing and writing, but I really had no idea what I was getting into.  Writing a series is a totally different thing than doing any one-off or a handful of sequels.  At least for right now, Clockwork Twist is the main focus of my life.  And today, 4 years in, I really can&#8217;t remember what life was like before I had Twist.  He just popped into my life one day and demanded to be.  Best surprise ever.</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-2617" src="http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/1-cake-01-300x275.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="275" srcset="http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/1-cake-01-300x275.jpg 300w, http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/1-cake-01-618x567.jpg 618w, http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/1-cake-01.jpg 1000w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" />Thanks to everyone who has been waiting for this release and sending me such lovely messages of encouragement!  You guys are awesome.  The best part  of this experience for me has to be all of the wonderful, generous, and supportive people I&#8217;ve met along the way!  I thought I was just going to write some books.  I never imagined I&#8217;d make so many friends because of Twist.</p>
<p>Isn&#8217;t that just deliciously ironic?  Twist just thought he was going to go repair a bit of clockwork when he first left London, after all.  Now I think I really know how he feels.</p>
<h4 style="text-align: center;">Happy Birthday Clockwork Twist!</h4>
<p>Here&#8217;s to another year of intrepid adventures, startling discoveries, and unexpected friends.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
